      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle reflects a showroom-quality aesthetic, featuring flawless exterior finishes and an interior that remains in pristine, original condition. Mechanical integrity is absolute, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its initial delivery. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this acquisition represents a rare opportunity to secure a vehicle of unrivaled caliber.",
